The 1500 square feet of warm comfort is surrounded in knotty pine, comfortable furnishings, and new cabinetry. It has warm gas heaters for those cool autumn nights.
You will find every convenience in the fully equipped kitchen, such as; refrigerator, range, washer and dryer, dishwasher, microwave, coffee maker, lobster pot, toaster, fans, and a grill.
It`s an ideal lake front home. It`s perfect for New England family vacations, romantic getaways, or winter holidays. Enjoy the morning sun`s glow on the lake from the picture windows or the balcony. Discover ever changing colors as the rising shadows glisten over the lake. This lovely vacation rental home offers magnificent views of the sunrise and romantic sunsets. The lake, forest, and mountain cast amazing, magical reflections of glowing reds and gold tones upon the pine ceiling and walls. The spacious living area, with its cathedral ceiling, skylights, and picture windows, frame the lake and landscape.

anticipated! The loft was beautiful and the cottage exuded warmth.
It felt so much like the way we view "Maine" and we were so sorry to
leave. We actually were going to leave late on Friday night to avoid
the Massachusetts Turnpike traffic, but decided to stay over, and
face the next day`s traffic because it was so hard parting with that
piece of heaven!
The lake, the cottage, the silence!, the trees, blueberries, fresh
water spring, fishing, canoes, and kayak were, in combination, almost
more than we deserved!
I can honestly say that this was the nicest cottage we have been to
in Maine and we have been visiting different areas every summer in
Maine for years, each time renting cottages (rarely renting the same

We met one of your neighbor`s who used to vacation in the area often
